The paper deals with a distributed sensor network and optimization of phase encoding parameters for minimizing estimation error. This involves techniques from information theory (cs.IT), control systems (cs.SY), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), multimedia (cs.MM), and signal processing (cs.SI). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
